{"text_id":87649,"tokens":["#"," How"," to"," Get"," Your"," Wife"," to"," Lose"," Weight","\n\n","As"," a"," partner",","," it","'","s"," natural"," to"," want"," your"," wife"," to"," be"," healthy"," and"," happy","."," However",","," approaching"," the"," topic"," of"," weight"," loss"," can"," be"," delicate"," and"," complex","."," It","\u2019","s"," important"," to"," express"," your"," concerns"," with"," sensitivity"," and"," support"," her"," through"," her"," journey","."," Below"," are"," some"," steps"," and"," considerations"," to"," keep"," in"," mind",".","\n\n","##"," Express"," Your"," Concerns"," About"," Her"," Health",","," If"," Appropriate","\n\n","Start"," by"," expressing"," your"," genuine"," concern"," for"," her"," health",","," rather"," than"," focusing"," on"," her"," appearance","."," Let"," her"," know"," you"," care"," about"," her"," well","-","being"," and"," want"," to"," support"," her"," in"," living"," a"," healthier"," life","."," Ensure"," your"," tone"," is"," loving"," and"," non","-","judgment","al"," to"," avoid"," her"," feeling"," attacked"," or"," criticized",".","\n\n","##"," Use"," Passive"," Measures",","," If"," Appropriate","\n\n","Sometimes",","," indirect"," encouragement"," can"," be"," effective","."," Introduce"," healthier"," cooking"," at"," home"," or"," suggest"," active"," dates"," instead"," of"," sedentary"," ones","."," This"," can"," help"," cultivate"," a"," healthier"," lifestyle"," without"," putting"," direct"," pressure"," on"," your"," wife",".","\n\n","##"," Avoid"," Judgment","al"," Language","\n\n","Language"," is"," powerful","."," Avoid"," using"," words"," that"," could"," be"," perceived"," as"," blaming"," or"," shaming","."," Phrases"," like"," \u201c","You"," need"," to"," lose"," weight","\u201d"," or"," \u201c","You"," should"," stop"," eating"," that","\u201d"," can"," cause"," her"," to"," feel"," defensive"," and"," hurt","."," Instead",","," use"," inclusive"," language"," such